      *****************************************************************
       510-ERRSET-SEC              SECTION.
      *
           MOVE    SPACE               TO  SPA-ERRMSG
      *
           EVALUATE    SPA-ERRCD
               WHEN    "0001"
                   MOVE    "診療内容が有りません"
                                       TO  SPA-ERRMSG
               WHEN    "0002"
                   MOVE    "ドクターが有りません"
                                       TO  SPA-ERRMSG
